338
00:29:31,320 --> 00:29:33,060
 Ne.

339
00:29:33,060 --> 00:29:33,980
 Ne.

340
00:29:33,980 --> 00:29:37,620
 I čak, ne bi uopće ulazila u teoriju u pozadini,

341
00:29:37,620 --> 00:29:40,660
