388
00:32:25,700 --> 00:32:28,700
 Gle, vinko je poslao mail samo meni.

389
00:32:28,700 --> 00:32:30,040
 Da.

390
00:32:33,040 --> 00:32:38,700
 Nedavno sam primijetio i jedan kreator na Instagramu

391
00:32:38,700 --> 00:32:43,400
